    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total gem. This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, keeping it garage-parked and detailed regularly. It\u2019s spotless inside and out, runs like a dream, and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
