      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously garaged and pampered, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, glass-like finish and zero imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, with supple leather, untouched trim, and that signature new-car scent. Every mechanical component has been maintained to the highest standard with a full, documented service history, ensuring a tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet driving experience. From the spotless engine bay to the unmarked alloy wheels, this is a rare opportunity to own a top-tier example of automotive excellence that satisfies even the most discerning eye.",
